OL,3,C'An assault on the rule of law':
OL,4,CStatement from Tamworth MP on violent
OL,5,Cdisorder
OL,7,FThe Labour MP for Tamworth has
OL,8,Fcondemned rioters who attacked the
OL,9,Ftown's Holiday Inn Express last night
OL,10,F(4th August).
OL,12,FStaffordshire Police has started an
OL,13,Finvestigation after an officer was
OL,14,Finjured in violence at the hotel.
OL,16,FPolice say a crowd of hundreds of
OL,17,Fprotesters gathered and starting
OL,18,Fattacking the hotel, with responding
OL,19,Fofficers faced with being attacked
OL,20,Fwith petrol bombs and fireworks.
