OL,3,C'An assault on the rule of law':
OL,4,CStatement from Tamworth MP on violent
OL,5,Cdisorder
OL,7,FA large-scale policing operation,
OL,8,Fsupported by colleagues from
OL,9,Fneighbouring police forces, was
OL,10,Fdeployed to the area after the crowd
OL,11,Fquickly became hostile.
OL,13,FSarah Edwards, the area's MP, released
OL,14,Fa statement on social media, which
OL,15,Fconfirmed that nobody inside the hotel
OL,16,Fwas injured.
OL,18,F"An assault on the rule of law"
