OL,3,C'An assault on the rule of law':
OL,4,CStatement from Tamworth MP on violent
OL,5,Cdisorder
OL,7,FShe wrote: "It is not protest. It's
OL,8,Fnot legitimate. It's a crime and
OL,9,Fviolent disorder. An assault on the
OL,10,Frule of law....
OL,12,F"This behaviour will not be tolerated
OL,13,Fon our streets. Tamworth is a
OL,14,Fwelcoming and caring community.
OL,16,F"Those who are intent on stoking
OL,17,Fdisorder and division are not welcome
OL,18,Fand do not speak for Britain or for
OL,19,FTamworth.
