OL,3,C'An assault on the rule of law':
OL,4,CStatement from Tamworth MP on violent
OL,5,Cdisorder
OL,7,F"It is fortunate that no one inside
OL,8,Fthe hotel was injured, but rest
OL,9,Fassured those involved in the violence
OL,10,Fwill face the full force of the
OL,11,Fjustice system".
OL,13,FShe earlier described the scenes in
OL,14,FTamworth on X as "shocking &
OL,15,Fdisgraceful" & are still ongoing",
OL,16,Fsaying "This will not be tolerated in
OL,17,Four town".
