OL,3,C'An assault on the rule of law':
OL,4,CStatement from Tamworth MP on violent
OL,5,Cdisorder
OL,7,FIn the speech Ms Edwards said: "In
OL,8,FTamworth the Holiday Inn has been used
OL,9,Ffor asylum purposes for years and the
OL,10,Fsimple reality is that residents want
OL,11,Ftheir hotel back. Tamworth benefits
OL,12,Ffrom local tourism and as I have said
OL,13,Fbefore in this Chamber, the Holiday
OL,14,FInn should be for holidays. I
OL,15,Ftherefore welcome (the) announcement
OL,16,Fthat the Border Security and
OL,17,FImmigration Bill includes plans to end
OL,18,Fasylum hotel use."
